The training and validation sets have exactly the same format, whereas some features are removed from the test set. These features are Article ID, Next read-time, Next Scroll Percentage, and Clicked Article IDs. Furthermore, to include beyond-accuracy computations, we have included 200,000 samples. Hence, the test set has an extra called is beyond-accuracy.
